{"tid":2159572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"脾氣差到核爆","createTime":"2020-08-16T11:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T11:45:46.000Z","uid":177873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0186b3dd6ebef27080aaf90e03707ef65b8a77a3","tid":2159572,"uid":177873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">脾氣差到爆嘅人真係唔好拍拖害人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郁啲就發脾氣 <br />\n狂鬧都算鳩數 <br />\n一唔啱佢意 又繼續屌<br />\n癲起上黎 會掟野 揼野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企道門個鎖頭已經比佢bam門<br />\nBam到壞撚埋<br />\n死物壞咗唔緊要<br />\n但個心臟真係頂唔緊<br />\n無啦啦又大叫發晒癲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係未試過坐低傾<br />\n但次次傾完都會有下一次<br />\n不停loop <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係拖友 係屋企人<br />\n無得quit"},{"pid":"246dd34f5ec112a1e95c857babf9d2c732e2df3d","tid":2159572,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"辛苦你了"}]}